  "title": "Polynomials - even functions",
  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div class=\"qti-layout-row\">\n<div class=\"qti-layout-col12\">\n<div class=\"prompt\">\n<p class=\"dap_body\">​A polynomial function has the form&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"p open parentheses x close parentheses equals a x to the power of j plus b x to the power of k\"><math alttext=\"p open parentheses x close parentheses equals a x to the power of j plus b x to the power of k\"><mi>p</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>j</mi></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>k</mi></msup></math></span>, where&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"a\"><math alttext=\"a\"><mi>a</mi></math></span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"b\"><math alttext=\"b\"><mi>b</mi></math></span>&nbsp;are nonzero constants,&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"j\"><math alttext=\"j\"><mi>j</mi></math></span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"k\"><math alttext=\"k\"> <mi>k</mi> </math></span>&nbsp;are nonnegative integers. Which of the following conditions guarantees that&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"p\"><math alttext=\"p\"><mi>p</mi></math></span>&nbsp;is an even function?</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n",
    "answer": "B-60271",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​<span aria-label=\"k equals 0\"><math alttext=\"k equals 0\"><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></p>",
        "value": "A-60270"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​<span aria-label=\"j equals 2 k\"><math alttext=\"j equals 2 k\"><mi>j</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>k</mi></math></span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"k\"><math alttext=\"k\"> <mi>k</mi> </math></span> is even.</p>\n",
        "value": "B-60271"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​<span aria-label=\"j plus k\"><math alttext=\"j plus k\"><mi>j</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>k</mi></math></span>&nbsp;is even.</p>",
        "value": "C-60272"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​<span aria-label=\"j times k\"><math alttext=\"j times k\"><mi>j</mi><mo>·</mo><mi>k</mi></math></span>&nbsp;is even.</p>",
        "value": "D-60273"
      }
